    <bf:title>
      <bf:Title>
	<bf:mainTitle>The integrated solution</bf:mainTitle>
	<bflc:nonSortNum>4</bflc:nonSortNum>
      </bf:Title>
    </bf:title>
    <bf:summary>
      <bf:Summary>
	<rdfs:label>Offers a learning system that teaches real-world business and organizational problem-solving skills. Introduces students to the educational versions of WordPerfect 4.2, VP-planner plus, and dBASE III plus, which are for use in conjunction with a data disk that contains 21 cases taken from both large and small business settings. The data disk also works with complete, professional versions of these programs.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:Summary>
    </bf:summary>
    <bf:tableOfContents>
      <bf:TableOfContents>
	<rdfs:label>Data disk -- WordPerfect version 4.2 -- VP-planner plus -- dBASE III plus (2 disks).</rdfs:label>
      </bf:TableOfContents>
    </bf:tableOfContents>
